						               													<description>Kill Monsters. Snag Treasure. Survive If You Can.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;RPG Battles: The Card Game, is a cards, dice, and strategy roleplaying game that is Pathfinder Roleplaying Game compatible.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players select a Character to play: Fighter, Monk, Paladin, Rogue, Ranger, or Sorceress. To start the game, each Player receives five random cards from the deck. Use these cards to configure your Character with additional weapons, armor, magic, or special events.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Gameplay consists of three phases:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Play cards: you may play as many cards from your hand as you wish.&amp;#10;     Draw a card: you must draw a card before you end your turn. If you draw a Monster or a trap, resolve combat. &amp;#10;     Discard: you may not hold more than five cards in your hand by the end of your turn. &amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players take damage to their Character from battling Monsters or by encountering traps. Playing cards allows you to buff up for battle, avoid dangerous situations, or heal lost health.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players take turns playing cards and fighting Monsters, while strategizing for best advantage. The last player standing wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
